<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="wash-v">wash <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /wɒʃ/    美 /wɑːʃ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>洗 (手、脸、身体等)；洗涤：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>wash</strong> clothes / <strong>dishes</strong> / a car
洗衣服 / 碗 / 车</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Wash your hands before eating.
吃东西前要先洗手。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My grandmother washes and irons every day.
我奶奶每天又洗又熨。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>耐洗：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Does this dress <strong>wash well</strong>?
这件连衣裙耐洗吗？</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.<strong>冲走；冲出：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Soil has been washed into the river from the riverbank or from the nearby fields.
河岸和附近田间的泥土被冲进了河里。</p><footer>2009 江苏改</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="wash-away">wash away</h3>
<p>1.<strong>冲掉；洗掉；消除…的影响：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The flood <strong>washed</strong> some of the houses <strong>away</strong> in the town.
洪水冲走了镇上的一些房屋。</p></div>

<h3 id="wash-off">wash off</h3>
<p>1.<strong>洗掉；洗去</strong>  </p>
<h3 id="wash-out">wash out</h3>
<p>1.<strong>洗净；清洗</strong>  </p>
<h3 id="wash-over">wash over</h3>
<p>1.<strong>（感觉）突然袭来：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A feeling of relief washed over me.
我顿时如释重负。</p></div>

<h3 id="wash-up">wash up</h3>
<p>1.<strong>(BrE) 洗餐具；(AmE) 洗手或洗脸：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It’s your turn to wash up today.
今天轮到你洗碗。</p></div></div>